getShadowShape

public MiPart getShadowShape()
Gets the shape of any shadow. Used by the shadow renderers. By default the shadow shape is null. Override and return the actual shape (perhaps MiiShadowRenderer.rectangularShadowShape) or null, which indicates to the shadow renderer that this part itself is to be the shape.
